tr: a deep and vivid red color
a transparent piece of ruby that has been cut and polished and is valued as a precious gem
a transparent deep red variety of corundum
used as a gemstone and in lasers
of a color at the end of the color spectrum (next to orange)
resembling the color of blood or cherries or tomatoes or rubies

value.def: A ruby is a dark red jewel.
Something that is ruby is dark red in colour.
